: The Lion, the Witch and the Wardrobe (1988)\nNot the End of the World (1989)\nFive Children and It (1991: aka The Sand Fairy on its American video release)\nArcher's Goon (1992)\nThe Return of the Psammead (1993: aka The Return of It on its American DVD release, and The Return of the Sand Fairy on its American video release)\nEarthfasts (1994)\nAgent Z and the Penguin from Mars (1996)", "biography_author": "Wikidata", "date_of_biography": "2023-09-05T22:42:57.788540+10:00", "external_links": [{"id": 6000, "uri": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marilyn_Fox"}], "uuid": "7a883d18-a51b-4076-a83c-5726f9eb9f58", "source": {"name": "Vernon", "slug": "vernon"}, "source_identifier": "24421", "external_references": [{"id": 51559, "source": {"name": "Wikidata", "slug": "wikidata"}, "source_identifier": "Q6763528"}, {"id": 55158, "source": {"name": "VIAF", "slug": "viaf"}, "source_identifier": "285749091"}], "date_modified": "2025-03-14T18:26:20.612971+11:00"}]}